criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Symptoms has appeared for at least 3 months;

          2. No organic disease and gastrointestinal alarm symptoms, which meet the diagnostic
             criteria of FGIDs;

          3. Sign informed consent and be able to read and understand the questionnaire.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. A history of organic gastrointestinal diseases;

          2. Alarm symptoms of digestive tract (such as melena, weight loss, fever, abdominal mass,
             ascites, anemia, family history of gastrointestinal tumors, etc.)

          3. Have a history of mental diseases;

          4. Unable to read and understand the questionnaire.
